e ou qu\u2019il faut se poser lors d\u2019une cr\u00e9ation de campagne publicitaire sur Meta Ads (Facebook et Instagram Ads). L\u2019int\u00e9r\u00eat et l\u2019avantage du social ads est le visuel, il est donc important donc de ne pas le n\u00e9gliger. Voici donc quelques axes qui vont vous aider \u00e0 pr\u00e9parer un brief complet et des visuels impactant.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"image-single-wrapper text-center\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/meta-ads.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Meta Ads\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/meta-ads.png 1920w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/meta-ads-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/meta-ads-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/meta-ads-1536x864.png 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row el_class=&#8221;content-article article-table-matiere&#8221;][vc_column]<div class=\"text-bloc toc\"><p class=\"titre_3\">Table des mati\u00e8res<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_74 ez-toc-wrap-center counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">Sommaire<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h1